📘 INTRODUCTION TO SOFTWARE PROJECT MANAGEMENT
Software Project Management (SPM) ka matlab hai software project ko plan, manage aur complete karna — time, cost aur quality ke andar.

👉 Simple language:
“Software banane ka poora process manage karna = SPM”

📌 1. Project Definition

Project kya hota hai?
👉 Project = Temporary kaam + specific goal

✔ Key Points:
Start aur end hota hai
Ek clear objective hota hai
Unique output deta hai (e.g., website, app)
🎯 Example:
College management system banana
E-commerce website banana

👉 Simple:
“Ek limited time me specific kaam complete karna = Project”

📌 2. Contract Management

Contract Management ka matlab hai:
👉 Client aur developer ke beech agreement handle karna
✔ Isme kya hota hai:
Project scope define karna
Budget fix karna
Timeline decide karna
Terms & conditions likhna
🎯 Example:
Client bolta hai:
Website 30 days me chahiye
Budget ₹50,000

👉 Tum contract banaoge:
Work kya hoga
Payment kaise milega
Delay hua toh kya hoga

👉 Simple:
“Client aur company ke beech ka legal agreement manage karna”

📌 3. Activities Covered by Software Project Management

SPM me kaun-kaun se kaam aate hai 👇

🔹 1. Planning
Kya banana hai?
Kaise banana hai?
🔹 2. Scheduling
Kaam kab hoga?
🔹 3. Resource Management
Team, tools, budget manage
🔹 4. Risk Management
Problem kya aa sakti hai?
🔹 5. Quality Management
Software sahi kaam kar raha hai?
🔹 6. Communication
Team aur client ke beech baat

👉 Simple:
“Project ko start se end tak control karne ke saare kaam”

📌 4. Overview of Project Planning

Project Planning = Project ka roadmap banana
✔ Planning me kya hota hai:
Requirements samajhna
Time estimate karna
Cost calculate karna
Team assign karna
🎯 Example:

Agar tum app bana rahe ho:
Design → 5 days
Backend → 10 days
Testing → 5 days

👉 Simple:
“Kaam shuru karne se pehle pura plan banana”

📌 5. Stepwise Project Planning

Ye ek structured method hai project plan karne ka 👇
🧩 Steps:
1. Identify Scope
👉 Project me kya include hai?
👉 Kya nahi hai?
2. Identify Objectives
👉 Goal kya hai?
Example:
Fast website
Secure login
3. Identify Project Infrastructure
👉 Tools & technology:
React, Node.js, Database
4. Identify Products & Activities
👉 Kya deliver karna hai?
UI
API
Database
5. Estimate Effort
👉 Kitna time lagega?

6. Identify Risks
👉 Problems kya aa sakti hai?
Server down
Developer leave
7. Allocate Resources

👉 Kaun kya karega?
Frontend dev
Backend dev
8. Review & Final Plan

👉 Sab check karo → final plan ready

👉 Simple:
“Step-by-step plan bana ke project ko smooth banana”

